cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on improving the communication efficiency of distributed training of neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of sketching methods is inspired by sub-linear/streaming algorithms, which suggests a potential connection to distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the convergence rates of Sketched SGD, which could be relevant to information theory (cs.IT) and neural networks (cs.NE).
